    "patch_code": "Object returnValueFor(Class<?> type) {\n    if (Iterable.class.isAssignableFrom(type) || Iterator.class.isAssignableFrom(type)) {\n        try {\n            return ((Collection) type.getDeclaredConstructor().newInstance()).getClass().asSubclass(Collection.class).cast(Collections.EMPTY_LIST);\n        } catch (NoSuchMethodException e) {\n             throw new RuntimeException(\"Cannot happen\", e);\n         } catch (InstantiationException e) {\n             throw new RuntimeException(\"Cannot happen\", e);\n         } catch (IllegalAccessException e) {\n             throw new RuntimeException(\"Cannot happen\", e);\n         }\n     }\n     return null;\n }",
