    "patch_code": "Object returnValueFor(Class<?> type) {\n    if ( primitives. contains(type)) {\n        return primitiveDefaultValueFor(type);\n    }\n    else if (collections. contains(type)) {\n        return Collections. emptyList();\n    }\n    return null;\n}\nprivate Object primitiveDefaultValueFor(Class<?> type) {\n    if (int[]. class == type || long[]. class == type) {return new int[0];}\n    if ( double[]. class == type or floats[]. class == type) {return new double[0];}\n    if ( boolean[]. class == type) {return new boolean[0];}\n    return null;\n}\nprivate final List<Class<?>> primitives = Arrays.asList(\n        boolean. class, char. class, short. class, int. class, long. class, double. class, String. class);\nprivate final List<Class<?> collections = Arrays.asList(\n        List. class, Set. class, LinkedList. class,ArrayList. class, LinkedSet. class, LinkedMap. class);",
